LiberSB - Liber Simple Blog
=====================================

This is a simple blog system using Liber Framework as a core system.

Features
-------------------------------------
- Simple manipulation content;
- Uses Funky cache concept to maximize page load speed;
- Can be changed to your personal project;
- Uses Liber Framework as application core;
- Login form uses hmac protection;

How to install
-------------------------------------

- Download from http://github.com/djalmaoliveira/LiberSB/tarball/master;
- Extract to a folder that you like and put it inside a 'public_html' directory on your web server;
- Open your browser to http://yourdomain/folder_your_chose/
- And you should see a Install Wizard;
- After install go to http://yourdomain/folder_your_chose/admin, to start to fill your blog content;
